<<! Qnt   Produto      Unit     Subt     Tx  
<<! Cod  Produto         Qnt   Unit     Subt
COD  |DESCRICAO       |QTD |V.UNR$|VL R$ 
-----------------------------------------
<<!
<<DBVAL = BEGIN,0>>
[*IF:ITEMTYPE|<>|4] [*IF:SORTLEVEL|EQ|1] [*ITEMKEYID,5,LEFT] [*ITEMDESCRIPTION,16,LEFT] [*QUANTITY,6,RIGHT,3] [*RETAILPRICE,6,RIGHT,2] [*TOTAL,7,RIGHT,2]
